claim.claim-text:
10. A portable electronic device charger comprising: 
a charger housing having a coupler portion adapted to engage a cigarette lighter power source and having a body portion; 
electrical contacts extending from said coupler portion and adapted to engage said cigarette lighter power source; 
an LED within said charger housing indicating said electrical contacts are in electrical engagement with said cigarette lighter power source; and 
a manual switch to selectively deactivate said LED.

22. A process for charging a portable electronic device comprising the steps of: 
electrically coupling a charger to a vehicle power supply; 
coupling said charger to said device; 
sensing a power supply voltage is greater than a preselected threshold; and 
metering current from said power supply to said device by way of said charger.
